original_title: Eleven-year-old Girl Defends Herself against Illegal Aliens  — The Donald
article_summary: Article debunks the claim of an 11-year-old girl defending herself against illegal aliens in Butte, Montana, as a fake story, with many commenters expressing their disbelief in its authenticity. The story was initially reported by Belleoffreedom and gained traction on social media.</s>
